Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_enable..._compatibility(25.10)    timing_enable..._compatibility(25.10)

Name
       timing_enable_all_fanin_fanout_levels_compatibility

Syntax
       timing_enable_all_fanin_fanout_levels_compatibility

       {true | false}

       Default: true

       Enables  computation of gate level count (for all_fanout/all_fanin com-
       mands) when an input pin is specified using the all_fanout -from  para-
       meter  and  output  pin is specified using the all_fanin -to parameter.
       When the initial gate is traversed, the count is computed as 1.

       When set to false, the global computes the gate level count as 0.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

